import React from 'react';
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom';
import App from './App';
import { BrowserRouter, Route, Routes } from 'react-router-dom'

ReactDOM.render(
    <BrowserRouter>
        <App />
        <Routes>
            <Route path="/signin" component={SigninScreen}></Route>
        </Routes>
    </BrowserRouter>,
    document.getElementById('root'))
